=====================================================================
EXAMPLE: If you pick "Back + Triceps + Neck" for Friday:
=====================================================================
  BACK (4 exercises):
    → 1 top compound by EMG rank (e.g. Barbell Row or Pull-up)
    → 3 more shuffled from the 34-exercise back pool

  TRICEPS (2 exercises):
    → 1 compound (e.g. Close-Grip Bench Press)
    → 1 isolation shuffled (e.g. Rope Pushdown or Skull Crusher)

  NECK (2 exercises):
    → 2 from the 7-exercise neck pool (e.g. Plate Neck Curl + Neck Harness)

  BONUS (2 exercises):
    → System auto-adds a random small muscle you didn't pick
      (e.g. calves → Standing Calf Raise + Seated Calf Raise)

  TOTAL: ~10 exercises + warm-up
=====================================================================


